title: Rep. Tom Emmer roasts Gary Gensler in fiery speech on the House floor
description:
Rep. Tom Emmer (R-MN) sharply criticized Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) Chair Gary Gensler in a speech on the House floor that condemned the agency’s approach to regulating digital assets. Emmer said Gensler had “proven himself to be ineffective and incompetent” through his aggressive enforcement actions while stressing that regulation was the preview of Congress. […]

title: Bitcoin Flips Ethereum for the First Time in 24-Hour NFT Sales Shift
description: On Wednesday, November 8, 2023, the Bitcoin blockchain saw its non-fungible token (NFT) asset sales surpass those on the Ethereum platform, marking a historic shift during a single-day span.
